<%= render 'shared/side_menu' %>
<h2>Flow Dashboard - "Find your flow, channel your best self"</h2>

<div id="graph" class="dashboard-section graph">
  <h3>Graph of Inputs</h3>
  <p>A 7 layered triangle each with 3 dimensions of flow.</p>
  
  <div class="overarching-flow-goal">
    <h4>Flow Goal - How do you wish to cultivate your energy and impact?</h4>
    <textarea id="flowGoal" placeholder="Enter your flow goal here" rows="3" style="resize: none;"></textarea>
    <div class="button-spacer"></div>
    <button onclick="saveFlowGoal()">Save Goal</button>
    <p id="currentFlowGoal"></p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="flow-triangle-container">
    <div id="flowPercentage" class="flow-percentage">0%</div>
    <svg width="200" height="200" viewBox="0 0 200 200">
      <polygon id="flowTriangle" points="100,10 10,190 190,190" fill="none" stroke="#444" stroke-width="10" />
      <polygon id="progressTriangle" points="100,10 100,10 100,10" fill="#64b5f6" stroke="none" />
    </svg>
  </div>

  <div class="flow-heuristics-container">
    <h4>Flow Categories - Low order to High order - How actualised is your Energy and Impact?</h4>
    <div class="flow-heuristics-grid">
      <div class="flow-heuristic">
        <h4>1. RESOURCEFUL</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Chemical</li>
          <li>Financial</li>
          <li>Physical</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="slider-container">
          <input type="range" id="flowHeuristic1" min="0" max="100" value="100">
          <span class="heuristic-value">100%</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-heuristic">
        <h4>2. VIBRATIONAL</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Electrical</li>
          <li>Signal</li>
          <li>Informational</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="slider-container">
          <input type="range" id="flowHeuristic2" min="0" max="100" value="100">
          <span class="heuristic-value">100%</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-heuristic">
        <h4>3. SUBJECTIVE</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Biological</li>
          <li>Mental</li>
          <li>Existential/Experiential</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="slider-container">
          <input type="range" id="flowHeuristic3" min="0" max="100" value="100">
          <span class="heuristic-value">100%</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-heuristic">
        <h4>4. IMPACTFUL</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Conditional</li>
          <li>Occupational</li>
          <li>Proficial/Skillful</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="slider-container">
          <input type="range" id="flowHeuristic4" min="0" max="100" value="100">
          <span class="heuristic-value">100%</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-heuristic">
        <h4>5. COLLECTIVE IMPACTFUL</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Technological</li>
          <li>Organisational</li>
          <li>Relational</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="slider-container">
          <input type="range" id="flowHeuristic5" min="0" max="100" value="100">
          <span class="heuristic-value">100%</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-heuristic">
        <h4>6. COMMUNITY IMPACTFUL</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Familial</li>
          <li>Cultural</li>
          <li>Transactional</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="slider-container">
          <input type="range" id="flowHeuristic6" min="0" max="100" value="100">
          <span class="heuristic-value">100%</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-heuristic">
        <h4>7. EVOLUTION IMPACTFUL</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Educational</li>
          <li>Adaptable</li>
          <li>Recreational</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="slider-container">
          <input type="range" id="flowHeuristic7" min="0" max="100" value="100">
          <span class="heuristic-value">100%</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="flowChart"></div>
</div>

<div id="practice" class="dashboard-section practice">
  <h3>Practice</h3>
  <p>Serving and helping others, and enabling ourselves to be more capable and competent to be able to help others.</p>
</div>

<div id="analogy" class="dashboard-section analogy">
  <h3>Analogy</h3>
  <p>A river of flow, with rocks of obstacles and bottlenecks hindering the flow. The flow is the energy that is moving through the total dimensions of our lives.</p>
</div>

<div id="equation" class="dashboard-section equation">
  <h3>Equation of Mastery</h3>
  <p>Mastery of Energy (I Act with Power) = (Maximise Efficiency + Minimise Waste) + (Process of Adapting * Inner Focus * Outer Impact)^Gratitude</p>
</div>

<div id="model" class="dashboard-section model">
  <h3>Model of Geometric Flow</h3>
  <p>Energy first flow of bowtie triangles where the middle energetic interface intersection is the emergence of the bowtie. Acts as a flywheel of energy momentum.</p>
</div>

<div id="metrics" class="dashboard-section metrics">
  <h3>Throughput Metrics for Flow</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Percentage of stages fully vibrant: <span id="vibrantPercentage">0</span>%</li>
    <li>Percentage of current priority stage fulfilled: <span id="priorityPercentage">0</span>%</li>
    <li>Next bottleneck or obstacle identified: <span id="bottleneckPercentage">0</span>%</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<style>
  body {
    padding-bottom: 0;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  body.form-open {
    padding-bottom: 300px; /* Adjust based on your form height */
  }
  .overarching-flow-goal {
    background-color: #2c2c2c;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 15px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    max-width: 100%; /* Changed from 600px to 100% */
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }
  .overarching-flow-goal h4 {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .overarching-flow-goal textarea {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 100%;
    padding: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    border: 1px solid #444;
    background-color: #1e1e1e;
    color: #ffffff;
    resize: vertical;
    box-sizing: border-box; /* Add this to include padding in width calculation */
  }
  .overarching-flow-goal button {
    background-color: #64b5f6;
    color: #000000;
    border: none;
    padding: 10px 15px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    cursor: pointer;
    width: 100px;
  }
  .overarching-flow-goal button:hover {
    background-color: #90caf9;
  }
  .overarching-flow-goal p {
    margin-top: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  .button-spacer {
    height: 10px;
  }
  .full-width {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .flow-triangle-container {
    position: relative;
    width: 200px;
    height: 200px;
    margin: 1rem auto;
  }
  .flow-percentage {
    position: absolute;
    top: -30px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
  .flow-heuristics-container {
    margin-top: 20px;
  }
  .flow-heuristics-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 15px;
  }
  .flow-heuristic {
    background-color: #2c2c2c;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 10px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    color: #ffffff;
  }
  .flow-heuristic h4 {
    margin: 0 0 5px 0;
    font-size: 0.9em;
  }
  .flow-heuristic ul {
    margin: 0 0 10px 0;
    padding-left: 20px;
  }
  .flow-heuristic li {
    font-size: 0.8em;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }
  .slider-container {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .slider-container input[type="range"] {
    flex-grow: 1;
    margin-right: 10px;
  }
  .heuristic-value {
    min-width: 40px;
    text-align: right;
  }
  .category-list {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .category-section {
    background-color: #2c2c2c;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: #ffffff;
  }
  .category-title {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .hexagon-container {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .hexagon-wrapper {
    width: 120px;
    height: 138px;
    margin: 10px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .hexagon {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: white;
    clip-path: polygon(50% 0%, 100% 25%, 100% 75%, 50% 100%, 0% 75%, 0% 25%);
    transition: background-color 0.3s, transform 0.2s;
    border: none;
    outline: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .hexagon:hover, .hexagon:focus {
    background-color: #e6f0ff;
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }
  .hexagon-content {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hexagon span {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    padding: 0 5px;
  }
  #domain-modal {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
    z-index: 1000;
  }
  #domain-modal::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }
  #domain-modal.hidden {
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  #domain-modal:not(.hidden) {
    opacity: 1;
    pointer-events: auto;
  }
  #domain-modal:not(.hidden)::before {
    opacity: 1;
  }
  #domain-modal > div {
    position: relative;
    max-height: 90vh;
    width: 90%;
    max-width: 500px;
    overflow-y: auto;
    background-color: white;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transform: scale(0.95);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, opacity 0.3s ease;
    z-index: 1001;
  }
  #domain-modal:not(.hidden) > div {
    transform: scale(1);
    opacity: 1;
  }
  #modal-content {
    padding: 2rem;
  }
  body.modal-open {
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .dashboard-section {
    background-color: #2c2c2c;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 15px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: #ffffff;
  }
</style>
